<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>朱家泓技術分析課程｜課前問卷分析報告</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+TC:wght@400;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --ink: #1a1410;
    --paper: #faf8f4;
    --accent: #c8872a;
    --accent-light: #f0d9b5;
    --accent-dark: #8b5e1a;
    --red: #c0392b;
    --green: #27ae60;
    --blue: #2c6fad;
    --muted: #6b5e52;
    --divider: #ddd5c8;
    --card-bg: #ffffff;
    --shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(26,20,16,0.08);
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
    background: var(--paper);
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  /* HEADER */
  .report-header {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
    padding: 64px 48px 48px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .report-header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; right: 0;
    width: 320px; height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, transparent 40%, rgba(200,135,42,0.15));
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .report-header .kicker {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.35em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .report-header .kicker::after {
    content: '';
    width: 40px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--accent);
  }
  .report-header h1 {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 44px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .report-header .subtitle {
    color: rgba(250,248,244,0.6);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .header-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 48px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .header-stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }
  .header-stat .num {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .header-stat .label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(250,248,244,0.55);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  /* LAYOUT */
  .container {
    max-width: 1140px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }

  .section {
    padding: 56px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--divider);
  }
  .section:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .section-title .num-badge {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: white;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 3px 9px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }
  .section-desc {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* GRID */
  .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; }
  .grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 20px; }
  .grid-4 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4,1fr); gap: 16px; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .grid-2, .grid-3, .grid-4 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .report-header { padding: 40px 24px 32px; }
    .header-stats { gap: 24px; }
  }

  /* CARDS */
  .card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--divider);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 28px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }
  .card-title {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--divider);
  }

  /* METRIC CARDS */
  .metric-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--divider);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 24px 20px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .metric-card .metric-val {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 38px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .metric-card .metric-label {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .metric-card.highlight {
    background: var(--ink);
    border-color: var(--ink);
  }
  .metric-card.highlight .metric-val { color: var(--accent); }
  .metric-card.highlight .metric-label { color: rgba(250,248,244,0.6); }
  .metric-card .metric-sub {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  /* BAR CHARTS */
  .bar-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
  .bar-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; }
  .bar-label-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
  }
  .bar-label {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .bar-count {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }
  .bar-track {
    background: var(--accent-light);
    border-radius: 2px;
    height: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: width 0.6s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);
  }
  .bar-fill.blue { background: var(--blue); }
  .bar-fill.green { background: var(--green); }
  .bar-fill.red { background: var(--red); }

  /* INTENT SCORE VISUAL */
  .intent-breakdown {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .intent-seg {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    min-width: 20px;
    transition: all 0.4s;
  }
  .intent-seg.s5 { background: #27ae60; }
  .intent-seg.s4 { background: #6abf69; }
  .intent-seg.s3 { background: #f0a500; }
  .intent-seg.s2 { background: #e67e22; }
  .intent-seg.s1 { background: #c0392b; }

  .intent-legend {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .intent-legend-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .legend-dot {
    width: 10px; height: 10px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* PAIN POINTS TABLE */
  .ranked-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
  .ranked-table th {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--divider);
    padding: 8px 12px;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .ranked-table td {
    padding: 12px 12px;
    font-size: 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--divider);
  }
  .ranked-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  .ranked-table .rank-num {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent-light);
    width: 40px;
  }
  .ranked-table tr:nth-child(-n+3) .rank-num { color: var(--accent); }
  .ranked-table .pct-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--accent-light);
    color: var(--accent-dark);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  /* PRICE ANALYSIS */
  .price-range-visual {
    position: relative;
    padding: 32px 0 16px;
  }
  .price-axis {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .price-marker {
    position: relative;
    height: 8px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--green), var(--accent), #e67e22, var(--red));
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .price-pin {
    position: absolute;
    top: -28px;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
  }
  .price-pin-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--muted);
    white-space: nowrap;
    background: var(--paper);
    padding: 1px 4px;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }
  .price-pin-dot {
    width: 12px; height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid white;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--divider);
  }
  .price-pin-dot.sweet { background: var(--accent); }
  .price-pin-dot.floor { background: var(--green); }
  .price-pin-dot.ceiling { background: var(--red); }

  /* INSIGHT CALLOUTS */
  .insight-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px,1fr)); gap: 16px; }
  .insight-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--divider);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 20px 20px 20px 24px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }
  .insight-card.action {
    border-left-color: var(--blue);
  }
  .insight-card.warning {
    border-left-color: var(--red);
  }
  .insight-card .insight-icon {
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .insight-card .insight-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .insight-card .insight-body {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* RECOMMENDATION CARDS */
  .rec-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--divider);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 24px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .rec-num {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 42px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent-light);
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 50px;
  }
  .rec-content {}
  .rec-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .rec-body {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .rec-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--accent-light);
    color: var(--accent-dark);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 2px 7px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  .report-footer {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: rgba(250,248,244,0.4);
    padding: 32px 48px;
    font-size: 12px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .report-footer strong { color: rgba(250,248,244,0.7); }

  /* HORIZONTAL RULE */
  hr { border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--divider); }

  /* BADGE */
  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }
  .badge-green { background: #d4f0e0; color: #1a7a42; }
  .badge-amber { background: #fcefd3; color: #9e6c00; }
  .badge-red { background: #fde0de; color: #a82020; }
  .badge-blue { background: #d6e8f8; color: #1d4d7e; }

  /* PROFILE PIE */
  .donut-wrap { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 24px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .donut-legend { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .donut-legend-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 12.5px;
  }
  .donut-legend-swatch {
    width: 12px; height: 12px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* QUOTE BLOCK */
  .quote-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px,1fr));
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }
  .quote-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--divider);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 20px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.65;
    position: relative;
  }
  .quote-card::before {
    content: '\201C';
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 48px;
    color: var(--accent-light);
    position: absolute;
    top: 8px;
    left: 14px;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .quote-card p {
    padding-top: 20px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .quote-card .quote-attr {
    margin-top: 8px;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--accent-dark);
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .summary-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--ink) 0%, #2d2520 100%);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 36px 40px;
    color: var(--paper);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .summary-box h3 {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .summary-box p {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(250,248,244,0.75);
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(16px); }
    to { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }
  }
  .section { animation: fadeInUp 0.4s ease both; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ===== HEADER ===== -->
<header class="report-header">
  <div class="kicker">ShiFu 課程分析報告</div>
  <h1>朱家泓技術分析課程<br>課前問卷分析報告</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">資料來源：課前問卷全量數據　|　分析完成：2026/03/06</p>
  <div class="header-stats">
    <div class="header-stat"><span class="num">303</span><span class="label">有效問卷數</span></div>
    <div class="header-stat"><span class="num">4.1</span><span class="label">平均購買意願（滿分5）</span></div>
    <div class="header-stat"><span class="num">75%</span><span class="label">高購買意願（4–5分）</span></div>
    <div class="header-stat"><span class="num">NT$3,000</span><span class="label">市場心理底價</span></div>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="container">

<!-- ===== SECTION 1: PURCHASE INTENT ===== -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="section-title">
    <span class="num-badge">01</span>
    購買意願分析
  </div>
  <p class="section-desc">問卷第5題：根據課程內容，您的購買意願？（1=極低 ～ 5=極高）</p>

  <div class="grid-4" style="margin-bottom:32px;">
    <div class="metric-card highlight">
      <div class="metric-val">4.1</div>
      <div class="metric-label">整體平均意願分數</div>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-card">
      <div class="metric-val" style="color:var(--green)">48%</div>
      <div class="metric-label">滿分 5 分（極高意願）</div>
      <div class="metric-sub">約 146 人</div>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-card">
      <div class="metric-val" style="color:var(--blue)">27%</div>
      <div class="metric-label">4 分（高意願）</div>
      <div class="metric-sub">約 82 人</div>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-card">
      <div class="metric-val" style="color:var(--red)">25%</div>
      <div class="metric-label">3 分以下（猶豫/低意願）</div>
      <div class="metric-sub">約 75 人</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">購買意願分布（5 → 1 由左至右）</div>
    <div class="intent-breakdown" id="intentBar">
      <div class="intent-seg s5" style="flex:146">5分 48%</div>
      <div class="intent-seg s4" style="flex:82">4分 27%</div>
      <div class="intent-seg s3" style="flex:51">3分 17%</div>
      <div class="intent-seg s2" style="flex:17">2分 6%</div>
      <div class="intent-seg s1" style="flex:7">1%</div>
    </div>
    <div class="intent-legend">
      <div class="intent-legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:#27ae60"></div>5分 – 立即購買意願強</div>
      <div class="intent-legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:#6abf69"></div>4分 – 有意購買、等確認</div>
      <div class="intent-legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:#f0a500"></div>3分 – 猶豫中、需更多資訊</div>
      <div class="intent-legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:#e67e22"></div>2分 – 觀望、有明確疑慮</div>
      <div class="intent-legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:#c0392b"></div>1分 – 無購買意願</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-top:24px;" class="insight-grid">
    <div class="insight-card">
      <div class="insight-icon">✅</div>
      <div class="insight-title">購買意願高度樂觀</div>
      <div class="insight-body">逾七成五受訪者評分 4 分以上，代表課程方向與定位對目標受眾的吸引力已相當強烈，是有利的市場訊號。</div>
    </div>
    <div class="insight-card warning">
      <div class="insight-icon">⚠️</div>
      <div class="insight-title">25% 猶豫族群有轉換空間</div>
      <div class="insight-body">3分以下（約75人）主要原因為「想知道更多資訊」、「不了解上課形式」、「不確認費用」，屬於可透過強化資訊轉換的潛在學員。</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-top:24px;" class="card">
    <div class="card-title">低購買意願主要原因（3分以下受訪者）</div>
    <div class="bar-list">
      <div class="bar-item">
        <div class="bar-label-row"><span class="bar-label">想知道更多資訊再決定</span><span class="bar-count">最多</span></div>
        <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill blue" style="width:58%"></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="bar-item">
        <div class="bar-label-row"><span class="bar-label">不了解上課形式</span><span class="bar-count">次多</span></div>
        <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill blue" style="width:32%"></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="bar-item">
        <div class="bar-label-row"><span class="bar-label">想確認費用再決定</span><span class="bar-count">第三</span></div>
        <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill blue" style="width:18%"></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="bar-item">
        <div class="bar-label-row"><span class="bar-label">課程內容不吸引／太難／太簡單</span><span class="bar-count">少數</span></div>
        <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill red" style="width:10%"></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="bar-item">
        <div class="bar-label-row"><span class="bar-label">只是填問卷支持老師開課</span><span class="bar-count">少數</span></div>
        <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill" style="width:7%"></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== SECTION 2: STUDENT PROFILE ===== -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="section-title">
    <span class="num-badge">02</span>
    學員樣貌分析
  </div>
  <p class="section-desc">投資經驗、年齡及性別結構分布</p>

  <div class="grid-2">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">投資經驗分布</div>
      <div class="bar-list">
        <div class="bar-item">
          <div class="bar-label-row"><span class="bar-label">有買個股，但沒有固定方法</span><span class="bar-count">~44%</span></div>
